OL,3,CCameras on Bluebird K7 show what her
OL,4,Cpilot hears
OL,6,FOn Monday May 11, 2026 history was
OL,7,Fmade: Donald Campbell's hydroplane
OL,8,FBluebird K7 returned to Coniston Water
OL,9,Ffor the first time since 1967.
OL,11,FOn-board camera footage has been
OL,12,Freleased giving the view from the
OL,13,Fcockpit as pilot Dave Warby took off
OL,14,Ffrom the jetty surrounded by hundreds
OL,15,Fof onlookers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
