OL,3,CCameras on Bluebird K7 show what her
OL,4,Cpilot hears
OL,6,FA few hours later, live on Lookaround,
OL,7,Fpilot Dave Warby told ITV Border
OL,8,Fpresenter Amy Lea: "(it) was a very
OL,9,Fspiritual feeling being in there
OL,10,Fbecause my father holds the unlimited
OL,11,Fwater speed record and I felt I had
OL,12,FDonald and my father in there with me.
OL,13,FAn incredible honour."
OL,15,FOrganisers of Bluebird K7 The Festival
OL,16,Fsaid they wanted the next generation
OL,17,Fto see and hear Bluebird again,
OL,18,Fbecause the sound is unique.
OL,26,@pD@UpmpD@Xpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
