OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778785871
OL,3,CCameras on Bluebird K7 show what her
OL,4,Cpilot hears
OL,6,FDave Warby said: "You don't really
OL,7,Fthink about the noise of it, you
OL,8,Freally think about the job at hand:
OL,9,Fmonitoring the boat and ensuring
OL,10,Fyou're looking after an iconic piece
OL,11,Fof history that has to go back in a
OL,12,Fmuseum."
OL,14,FOn day two of the festival, Tuesday
OL,15,FMay 12, it was widely anticipated that
OL,16,FK7 would not be able to run due to
OL,17,Fweather conditions from early morning.
OL,18,FOrganisers confirmed by lunchtime that
OL,19,Fit was too windy to bring Donald
OL,20,FCampbell's historic hydroplane onto
OL,21,FConiston.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
