PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778785871
OL,3,CCameras on Bluebird K7 show what her
OL,4,Cpilot hears
OL,6,FThe crowd of spectators is smaller
OL,7,Fthan the day before but hundreds of
OL,8,Fpeople still came out to wait for a
OL,9,Fweather window for another historic
OL,10,Fmoment.
OL,12,FIt was hoped the hyrdocraft
OL,13,Fcommissioned by Campbell's father, Sir
OL,14,FMalcolm Campbell in 1937, would take
OL,15,Fto the water. Coniston is famously the
OL,16,F"home" of the Campbell family's speed
OL,17,Frecords, but this would actually be
OL,18,FBluebird K3 making its debut on these
OL,19,Fwaters.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
